| Plot                    = While investigating a wax museum, Spider-Man finds himself being attacked by wax figures of the Avengers and famous people from the past and present. It's revealed that this is the work of Mysterio and, after defeating him, Spider-Man is recruited by Spider-Punk to help other Spider-Men save the Multiverse.

| Cast                    = * Griffin Burns as [[Peter Parker (Earth-17628)|Spider-Man]]
* Jake Eberle as [[Hobart Brown (Earth-138)|Spider-Punk]]

| Notes                   = * Art by [[Dario Brizuela]] and colors by [[Rachelle Rosenberg]].[[Category:Dario Brizuela/Penciler]][[Category:Dario Brizuela/Inker]][[Category:Rachelle Rosenberg/Colorist]]
| Trivia                  = * The wax statues of Thor and Green Goblin use the characters' designs from ''[[Ultimate Spider-Man (animated series)|Ultimate Spider-Man]]'' ([[Earth-12041]]) due to to the characters not having appeared in the continuity of ''[[Marvel's Spider-Man (animated series)|Marvel's Spider-Man]]'' ([[Earth-17628]]) at the time of this short's release.
